data.description: YOU JUST FOUND YOUR NEXT PLACE TO CALL HOME!! For sale is this charming 3 bed 1 bath brick ranch home!! Located on a quiet dead end street. Convenient location near shopping, public library, restaurants etc. Harwood floors throughout most of the main floor. Kitchen was updated by the previous owner and the stove is only 1 year old. The deck is conveniently located just off the kitchen area which is a great area for those summer barbecues along with your morning cup of coffee to start your day. Most of the main floor has been freshly painted. Roof, gutters, siding and soffit are only 1 year old! Basement is partially finished, has a rough in for a 1/2 bath, and is a walkout. Home backs to the woods. There is a patio area in the rear of the home which is great for entertaining purposes etc. Home is in move in condition so move right in and enjoy! Seller is providing a One Year Choice Home Warranty! Schedule your appointment today before this opportunity passes you by!
